reviewText: Product in great condition.  Prompt delivery.  Very helpful.  Thank you.

Another wonderful gathering of Candid Camera episodes - On those days you just want to laugh out loud, I highly recommend this show.  ALL ages would like this - great family show.  We always watched it years ago on television.  Allen Funt is a genius!!

First, humor is 100% individual.  We don't all think the same thing is funny.

It is called the best of....some parts were good, but most of my favorites were not included.  I probably need more of the episodes to get my favorites.  Other people will love it, we're all different.
I don't like to write a lot of words. I just want to thank you for your service and for a great product. thank you. Sincerely Linda Johnson

The seller sent this out quickly, which I appreciated.
Some of the video was quite entertaining, however, I remember seeing some of the Candid Camera shots from earlier days that in my mind were a lot funnier than the ones on this video.
